<nav class="nav" id="nav" data-screen-label="Nav"><svg class="sunmark" viewBox="0 0 32 32" aria-hidden="true"><circle class="sun-disc" cx="16" cy="16" r="10"></circle></svg><a class="wm" href="/">AMPM <small>BUILDING SERVICES</small></a><div class="links"><a href="/services/" class="">Services</a><a href="/work/" class="">Work</a><a href="/compliance/" class="">Compliance</a><a href="/about/" class="">About</a><a href="/contact/" class="">Contact</a></div><a class="phone" href="tel:03300430080">0330 043 0080</a></nav><div class="page" style="--svc: var(--m-purple);"><div class="shell"><section class="sec p-hero"><div class="reveal in"><span class="svc-bar" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span></div><div class="reveal in"><div class="kicker">Commercial Fit-out</div></div><h1 class="reveal d1 in">Category B Fit-out</h1><p class="lede reveal d2 in">Category B fit-out across London and the South East — the occupier fit-out that turns a Cat A shell into a working space. Partitions, joinery, meeting rooms, branding and FF&amp;E, with the M&amp;E coordinated in-house so the services and the fabric never fall between two trades.</p><div class="reveal d3 in" style="margin-top: 28px;"><a class="btn line sm" href="/contact/">Enquire about Category B Fit-out →</a></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 32px;"><div class="kicker">What we deliver</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Category B Fit-out,<br>self-delivered.</h2></div><div class="capgroups reveal in"><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span><span>Scope</span></h4><ul><li>Partitions, dry-lining &amp; glazed screens</li><li>Bespoke joinery, reception &amp; tea-points</li><li>Meeting rooms, breakout &amp; collaboration space</li><li>Branding, graphics &amp; feature finishes</li><li>FF&amp;E coordination &amp; furniture install</li><li>Occupier fit-out on top of a Cat A base</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span><span>Standards &amp; compliance</span></h4><ul><li>CDM 2015 across every package</li><li>Building Regulations Part B — fire safety</li><li>Building Regulations Part E — acoustics, and Part M — access</li><li>BS 9999 &amp; BS 9991 — fire safety in the design of buildings</li><li>BS 8000 — workmanship on building sites</li></ul></div></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;"><div class="kicker">FAQs</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Your questions,<br>answered.</h2></div><div class="faq reveal in"><details class="faq-item"><summary>What does a Category B fit-out cover?</summary><p>Cat B is the occupier fit-out: partitions, joinery, meeting rooms, branding, finishes and FF&amp;E built on top of the Cat A base. It's where the space becomes the tenant's — laid out to how the team actually works, to the move-in date that has to hold.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Can you take a floor from Cat A through to Cat B?</summary><p>Yes. We deliver both Cat A and Cat B, and the transition between them — so the lettable shell and the occupier fit-out run as one programme under one accountable team rather than a handover between contractors.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>How do you hold the move-in date?</summary><p>We pin long-lead items and FF&amp;E at design stage, procure early and run a buildable programme with one project manager accountable for it. The move-in date is the fixed point we plan the whole fit-out back from.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Which areas do you cover?</summary><p>London and the South East, including Sussex, Surrey, Kent, Hampshire and Berkshire.</p></details></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;"><div class="kicker">Part of Commercial Fit-out</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Explore the full<br>package.</h2></div><div class="sectorrow reveal in"><a class="secto